@jthestness @poxvoculi : Any suggestions here? 

It seems to be complaining about not finding `ompi_datatype_t* tensorflow::contrib::mpi_collectives::MPIType<int>()`, which should be defined in `ring.cc`.

Just to be clear: You did build from sources using the instructions in [`contrib/mpi/README.md`](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/mpi/README.md), right?
